title: Week 3 Recap: Breaking Down the 3-0 Teams and Winners and Losers | The Ringer NFL Show
description:
Kevin Clark and Nora Princiotti break down each 3-0 team (3:25). Then they go through their Week 3 winners and losers (47:42), answer some listener questions (01:13:14), and finish up with the Clickbait Headline of the Week (01:19:03).

Hosts: Kevin Clark and Nora Princiotti
